import React from 'react'
import Imgslider from './ImgSlider'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import Categoryshow from './Categoryshow'
import Login from './Login';

const MainPage = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <BrowserRouter>
      
    <Routes>
    <Route path="/" element={ <Imgslider/>} />
    <Route path="women" key={'women'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="men" key={'men'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="kids" key={'kids'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="perfume" key={'perfume'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="login" key={'login'} element={ <Login/> } />
    <Route path="contact" key={'contact'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="signup" key={'signup'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="signup" key={'signup'} element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  )
}

export default MainPage
